snippet.title: Amber Heard CONFIRMS relationship with billionaire Elon Musk ! Hot News
snippet.description:
Amber Heard CONFIRMS relationship with billionaire Elon Musk as she shares 'cheeky' snap with her lipstick on his face.
Amber Heard has seemingly confirmed her relationship with billionaire Elon Musk with a fun Instagram picture of them at dinner in Australia with her lipstick on his cheek.
She drew attention to the lip-marking in the photo by captioning it: 'Cheeky.' 
It seemed to be an intimate affair as they sat at a dinner table alongside each other while Amber placed her hand on the shoulder of the 45-year-old Tesla inventor and entrepreneur.
